  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Person with CP, GMFCS-level I-IV, age 10-17 years

          -  Living in Mid-Norway

          -  Wants to increase his / her level of physical activity

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Completes less than 75% of the total number of training sessions

          -  Not able to complete the testing and training procedures due to sickness, injury or
             other physical and psychological conditions
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
